[{"id":"VR803403","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two spheres connected by a wire. The left sphere is larger, has a charge uppercase Q sub 0 and a radius uppercase R. The second sphere is smaller, and has a radius lowercase r.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR803403.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A metal sphere with radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase R\"><math alttext=\"uppercase R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>R</mi></math></span></span> is given an initial charge of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase Q sub 0\"><math alttext=\"uppercase Q sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mstyle></math></span></span>. A second, smaller and neutral, metal sphere with radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lowercase r\"><math alttext=\"lowercase r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>r</mi></math></span></span>, such that <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase R is equal to a times lowercase r\"><math alttext=\"uppercase R is equal to a times lowercase r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi></math></span></span>, where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a is greater than 1\"><math alttext=\"a is greater than 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>a</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>, is placed far away from the first sphere. A wire connects the two spheres, as shown, until equilibrium is reached. The charge on the smaller sphere is then <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lowercase q\"><math alttext=\"lowercase q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>q</mi></math></span></span>. Which of the following represents the fraction <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction lowercase q over uppercase Q sub 0\"><math alttext=\"the fraction lowercase q over uppercase Q sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mi>q</mi><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mfrac></math></span></span>?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR803403_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction a over a plus 1\"><math alttext=\"the fraction a over a plus 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction 1 over a plus 1\"><math alttext=\"the fraction 1 over a plus 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a\"><math alttext=\"a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>a</mi></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction 1 over a\"><math alttext=\"the fraction 1 over a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>a</mi></mfrac></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":1}]